The appearance of the subsun can vary, but it often looks like a glowing patch of light mirroring the sun's position. It moves with your perspective because it's dependent on the alignment of the ice crystals relative to your viewing angle. This phenomenon is part of the broader family of halo effects, which includes sundogs, halos, and light pillars.

Subsun sightings are rare but beautiful, often adding a magical quality to high-altitude views!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gE52E3G</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LosPer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Princess Prowess</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rzCEspn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VgdnoGu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kqQpNS3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6DhsMqn.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M5WqO62.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rzCEspn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheWoodsAreVile]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>In case you haven’t seen a diving piglet yet today</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RjJpddh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xZfMjP5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RjJpddh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[luvdechub]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Are you ... are you ... really? Moooooooom.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/I9wyMAI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5Q0kEiK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/I9wyMAI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dude has it right!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2A66jDH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7BPSSve.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid